{"tid":2461161,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《路透社》稱港府要求12個國家不承認BNO護照","createTime":"2021-03-25T09:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T09:57:21.000Z","uid":54800,"like":25,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"c31fbe2c5bb529c67e039108820119b718b43a38","tid":2461161,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:16:37.000Z","msg":"《路透社》報道，特區政府向大約12個國家的領事館發信，要求不承認英國國民(海外)護照BNO作為申請工作假期簽證的證件，要求以特區護照取代。<br />\n<br />\n一名西方高級外交官員對《路透社》表示，大部分國家會忽視有關要求，指出香港無權要求外國承認哪一本護照。另一位外交人員則形容舉動挑釁，不是香港政府的慣常做法。<br />\n<br />\n香港現時與14個國家達成工作假期協議，《路透社》說，美國、日本、南韓、意大利、新西蘭、芬蘭和挪威都表示繼續承認BNO。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，未知美國是否收到信件，但國務院回覆說，BNO仍然是有效的申請簽證和旅遊證件。匈牙利回覆說收到信件，開始就簽證安排談判；南韓當局說未有收到信件。"},{"pid":"aa17552570180faa2d8adf11b9c9a47a5a5780a1","tid":2461161,"uid":54800,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1582552_1_L_20210325164621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1582552_1_L_20210325164621.jpg&h=2cf1e9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共而家做埋外交交涉動作???<br />\n反了反了~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ed0f437ab87b6b1173ac8461378d484d7db0a1","tid":2461161,"uid":2419,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:26:12.000Z","msg":"呢d就真正干涉別國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b2b1ff9f35be1ba7860baf0fe9facb14f26fb8","tid":2461161,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73cb48e5870423046438d7828a506a45ae3a3db","tid":2461161,"uid":261937,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"伊朗，北韓，痿內瑞拉，重有無？"},{"pid":"586d772b90a8c774d534fdd1deb4d90180243825","tid":2461161,"uid":197569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy"